718465f-a.title: Manhattan: Central Park West - 70th Street
718465f-a.text:
Central Park West, west side, from 71st to 70th Streets. At the
extreme left may be seen the Portuguese synagogue, Congregation
Shearith Israel. In the foreground is a portion of Central Park.
February 2, 1929.
P. L. Sperr, Photographer.
